text: hi sprinkles! casey and I spent some time talking through project components this morning, and casey got some code written for the user class and the enrollment functionality. I started outlining some TODOs in CourseController and then hit a wall (how do we build the plane while we’re flying it?! my brain!) so I thought I’d hop on the front-end but ran into some issues with it. I thought I’d start fresh with a new React app since we hadn’t touched that yet.
